wallet.description: Iwaleti ekhuselekileyo yeemali ezininzi enokulandelwa kwebhalansi yexesha langempela, imbali yentengiselwano, kunye nezakhono zokufaka/ukutsala ngokungenakunqandwa.
wallet.title: Wallet Management

transactions.title: Imbali yeNtengiselwano
transactions.description: Iirekhodi ezithe vetshe zentengiselwano ezinokuhluza okuphucukileyo, izakhono zokuthumela ngaphandle, kunye neendlela zokuhlola ezibanzi zazo zonke izinto zemali.

transfers.title: Ukudluliselwa
transfers.description: Iinkonzo zokudluliselwa kwangaphakathi nangaphandle kunye nokuqhutywa ngoko nangoko, imirhumo ekhuphisanayo, kunye nenkxaso yeemali ezininzi.

investments.title: Utyalo-mali
investments.description: Amathuba ahlukeneyo otyalo-mali kunye nohlahlelo lomgangatho wobungcali, izixhobo zokuhlola umngcipheko, kunye nokulandelwa kokusebenza kwiindidi ezininzi zee-asethi.

plans.description: Izicwangciso zotyalo-mali ezilungiselelweyo ezineeprofayili zomngcipheko ezithe vetshe, idatha yokusebenza yembali, kunye nemigaqo eguquguqukayo ukuze ihambelane neenjongo zakho zemali.
plans.title: Investment Plans

staking.title: Imivuzo ye-Staking
staking.description: Fumana ingeniso engasebenziyo ngokufaka i-cryptocurrency kunye namazinga e-APY akhuphisanayo, amaxesha okutshixa aguquguqukayo, kunye nokusasazwa okuzenzekelelayo kwemivuzo.

ico.description: Ukufikelela kwangethuba kwi-Initial Coin Offerings ezihlolwe ngengqiqo kunye neengxelo zophando olubanzi lwe-due diligence, uhlalutyo lwe-tokenomics, kunye nokulandelwa kotyalo-mali.
ico.title: Token Sales

marketplace.title: Indawo yoRhwebo
marketplace.description: Hlola iindawo zokurhweba zedijithali neziphathekayo ezikumgangatho ophezulu ngokuthengiselana okukhuselekileyo, abathengisi abaqinisekisiweyo, kunye nokukhusela abathengi okubanzi.

nft.description: Fumanisa, udala, kwaye urhwebe nge-asethi zedijithali ezikhethekileyo kwindawo yethu ye-NFT ekhethiweyo enezakhono zokufaka ibhidi kunye nemali yomqambi.
nft.title: NFT Marketplace

store.title: Ivenkile
store.description: Indawo yokurhweba ekumgangatho ophezulu enezinto zedijithali neziphathekayo ezikhuselekileyo zokuhlawula, ukuthunyelwa kwihlabathi lonke, kunye nokukhusela abathengi.

services.title: Iinkonzo
services.description: Iinkonzo zobungcali nezixhobo zokuphucula amava akho orhwebo, kubandakanywa iinkqubo ze-affiliate, izixhobo zemfundo, kunye nenkxaso ephezulu.

affiliate.description: Yenza imali kwintamanzi yakho ngenkqubo yethu ebanzi ye-affiliate eneekhomishini ezikhuphisanayo, ukulandela kwexesha langempela, kunye nezixhobo zentengiso.
affiliate.title: Affiliate Program

support.title: Iziko leNkxaso
support.description: Inkxaso yabathengi yobungcali enolawulo lwetikiti, izakhono zencoko ephilileyo, kunye nokulawulwa kwe-akhawunti ezinikeleyo kubasebenzisi abaphezulu.

faq.description: Amaxwebhu abanzi, izifundo, kunye nemibuzo ebuzwa rhoqo ukukunceda ukwandisa izakhono zeqonga.
faq.title: Knowledge Base

merchant.title: Merchant Gateway
merchant.description: "Accept payments from customers through our secure payment gateway with API integration and real-time transaction tracking.

insights.title: Iingqiqo
insights.description: Uhlalutyo lweemarike zobungcali, iingqiqo zorhwebo, kunye neendaba zeshishini kwiqela lethu leengcali zemali kunye nabaphandi beemarike.
